rt-value=\"2018-10-04\"| 1\u20134 Oct 2018\n| 2,200\n| 8.4\n| style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''28.3'''\n| 4.4\n| 8.4\n| 4.6\n| 19.7\n| 6.0\n| 18.8\n| 1.4\n| style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 8.6\n|-\n| Demoskop<ref>{{cite web |title=St\u00f6det f\u00f6r L\u00f6fven v\u00e4xer i f\u00f6rsta m\u00e4tningen efter valet |url=https://www.expressen.se/nyheter/val-2018/stodet-for-lofven-vaxer-i-forsta-matningen-efter-valet/ |language=Swedish |work=Expressen |date=4 October 2018}}</ref>\n| data-sort-value=\"2018-10-02\"| 25 Sep\u20132 Oct 2018\n| 1,616\n| 7.7\n| style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''30.6'''\n| 3.5\n| 8.7\n| 4.8\n| 18.8\n| 6.1\n| 18.0\n| 1.8\n| style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 11.8\n|-\n| Sifo<ref>{{cite web |title=V\u00e4ljarbarometer Rapport 20181003 |url=https://www.kantarsifo.se/sites/default/files/reports/documents/kantarsifovb_3_oktober_2018.pdf |language=Swedish |work=Kantar Sifo |date=3 October 2018}}</ref>\n| data-sort-value=\"2018-10-02\"| 24 Sep\u20132 Oct 2018\n| 8,108\n| 7.8\n| style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''28.5'''\n| 4.3\n| 8.8\n| 5.3\n| 19.2\n| 6.4\n| 18.3\n| 1.3\n| style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 9.3\n|- style=\"background:#E9E9E9;\"\n| [[2018 Swedish general election|2018 election]]\n| data-sort-value=\"2018-09-09\"| 9 Sep 2018\n| \u2013\n| 8.0\n| style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''28.3'''\n| 4.4\n| 8.6\n| 5.5\n| 19.8\n| 6.3\n| 17.5\n| 1.6\n| style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 8.4\n|}\n\n== Municipal polls ==\n\n=== Graphical summary ===\n[[File:Municipal opinion polls in Sweden 2018-2022 chart.png]]\n\n\n=== Vote Share ===\n<!-- Only add non-incumbent parties if they have had a poll above the 4 % threshold. -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:90%;line-height:14px;\"\n|- style=\"height:40px;\"\n! rowspan=\"