ly Furtado album)|Loose]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Nelly Furtado]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |{{Flagu|Canada}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''10.0'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref name=\"billboard2\">{{cite web|url=https://books.google.hr/books?id=XFZj6BL4zl8C&pg=PA24&lpg=PA24&dq=nelly+furtado+folklore+2+million+worldwide|title=Five Rings To Rule Them All\n|publisher= Billboard|page=24|first=Jen|last=Qilson|date=1 August 2008|accessdate=17 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2010\n|''[[Recovery (Eminem album)|Recovery]]''\n|[[Eminem]]\n|{{Flagu|United States}}\n|'''10.0'''\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2012/oct/29/eminem-new-album-baseball-cap|title=Eminem teases new album \u2013 on a baseball cap|last=Michaels|first=Sean|date=2012-10-29|work=The Guardian|access-date=2019-06-12|issn=0261-3077}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2002\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Stripped (Christina Aguilera album)|Stripped]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Christina Aguilera]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |{{Flagu|United States}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''10.0'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref name=\"wwsales\">{{cite web|url=http://www.vh1la.com/musica/artistas/christina-aguilera/|title=Biograf\u00edas de artistas: Christina Aguilera|work=[[VH1 Latin America]]|accessdate=August 26, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331194116/http://www.vh1la.com/musica/artistas/christina-aguilera/#bio|archivedate=March 31, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.leparisien.fr/loisirs-et-spectacles/christina-aguilera-c-est-bien-ce-soir-24-10-2003-2004491755.php|title=Christina Aguilera, c'est bien ce soir|work=[[Le Parisien]]|first=Emmanuel|last=Marolle|date=October 4, 2013|accessdate=August 26, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2005\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Confessions on a Dance Floor]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Madonna (entertainer)|Mado