-Disney-Records-High-School-Musical-Audio#.U8BbU5RdWSo |title=Walt Disney Records\u2019 High School Musical Audio Franchise Makes Global Chart History for Second Consecutive Year|publisher=[[Business Wire]] |date=June 16, 2008 |accessdate=July 6, 2014}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#EEF7FF\"\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2007\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[High School Musical 2 (soundtrack)|High School Musical 2]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Various Artists\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''6.0'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/global/1307169/high-school-musical-takes-global-top-spot-in-07 |title='High School Musical' Takes Global Top Spot In 07|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |date=June 17, 2008 |accessdate=July 6, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2008\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[Viva la Vida or Death and All His Friends]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Coldplay]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''5.8'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/section_news/20090216.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090624051531/http://www.ifpi.org/content/section_news/20090216.html |title=Viva La Vida top selling global album of 2008|publisher=[[IFPI]] |archivedate=June 24, 2009 |date=February 16, 2009|accessdate=July 6, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2009\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[I Dreamed a Dream (album)|I Dreamed a Dream]]'' \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Susan Boyle]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''6.4'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/section_news/20100428.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527214408/http://www.ifpi.org/content/section_news/20100428.html |title=IFPI publishes Rec