18.pdf}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#EEF7FF\"\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2018\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[The Greatest Showman (soundtrack)]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Various Artists\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''3.5'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{citation|contribution=Global Top 10 Albums of 2018|page=11|url=https://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2019.pdf |title=IFPI Global Music Report 2019|publisher=[[IFPI]] |date=2019 |accessdate=April 30, 2019|format=PDF}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2019\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[5x20 All the Best!! 1999\u20132019]]''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Arashi]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{Flagu|Japan}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''3.3'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ifpi.org/news/ARASHI-Awarded-Global-Album-of-2019-for-their-20th-anniversary-compilation|title=ARASHI Awarded Global Album of 2019 for Their 20th Anniversary Compilation 5x20 All the BEST!! 1999-2019|publisher=[[IFPI]]|date=March 19, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of best-selling albums]]\n* [[List of best-selling albums in the United States]]\n* [[List of best-selling albums by country]]\n* [[List of best-selling music artists]]\n* [[List of best-selling singles]]\n* [[Best-selling albums in the United States since Nielsen SoundScan tracking began]]\n* [[List of best-selling albums by year in the United States]]\n* [[List of best-selling Latin albums in the United States]]\n* [[Global Recording Artist of the Year|IFPI Global Recording Artist of the Year]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Lists of best-selling albums}}\n\n[[Category:21st century in music|Best-selling albums]]\n[[Category:21st century-related lists|Best-selling albums]]\n[[Category:Lists of best-selling albums|21st century]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis is a '''list of the best-selling albums of the 21st century''', based on [[IFPI]] certification and [[Nielsen SoundScan]] sales tracking. The criteria are that the album must have been published (including self-publishing by the artist), and the album must have shipped at least 10 million units [[21st century|starting from January 1, 2001]].\nUnits sold include [[Compact disc|physical copies]] and [[Downloading|digital downloads]].<!--DO NOT CHANGE the sales unless you can give a reliable source that indicates the number-->\n\nWith sales of over 32 million copies; \n[[Adele|Adele's]] [[21 (Adele album)|21]] is the best selling album of the 21st century.\n\n== Legend ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n |-\n ! colspan=\"2\" | Colors\n |-\n | style=\"background:#FFFFFF; width:20px;\" |\n | Studio albums\n |-\n | style=\"background:#FAFAD2; width:20px;\" |\n | Greatest hits and compilations\n |-\n | style=\"background:#E7FEFF; width:20px;\" |\n | Soundtracks\n |}\n\n==30 million copies or more==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%; text-align:center;\"\n|+\n!style=\"width:10%;\"|Year\n!style=\"width:25%;\"|Album\n!style=\"width:25%;\"|Artist/s\n!style=\"width:20%;\"|Nationality\n!style=\"width:15%;\"| Worldwide sales<br><small>(in millions)</small>\n!style=\"width:1%;\"|Ref(s)\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2011\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[21 (Adele album)|21]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Adele]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |{{Flagu|United Kingdom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''32.0'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref name=\"wwsales2017\">{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-people-adele-idUSKBN12V20I |title=Adele says she battled depression, before and after son's birth|last= Serjeant|first=Jill|editor-last=Osterman|editor-first=Cynthia|date=31 October 2016|work=[[Vanity Fair (magazine)|Vanity Fair]]|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=14 February 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==20\u201329 million copies==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style